<plot>In every life there is a moment at which you ask yourself, "Is this all there is?" David Ashley is at that point. So he quits his commercial art job to pursue his dream of becoming a fine art painter. He soon discovers there is no sharp line between art and commerce. A light family drama told with warmth and charm.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?420519</url></doc>
